de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim

Class PhysicalHarborStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim.PhysicalHarborStorage

  • public class PhysicalHarborStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the abstraction of the "physical harbor storage", into which the crane actually puts storage elements. It provides a static method to create a new physical harbor storages and a method to retrieve the PhysicalCrane object associated with this physical harbor storage It provides methods to retrieve a list or an array of available storage places. This method(s) are the only way to get information about the physical storage places within the harborg storage. Use one of them!
    Author:
    Weigel
